</refsynopsisdiv>
<refsect1>
<title>Description</title>
<para>
png_set_filter() shall set the filtering method used for scan-line filtering.
The only valid value for "method" is 0. "filters" is a bitmap for which the
following bits may be set.
PNG_NO_FILTERS
PNG_FILTER_NONE
PNG_FILTER_SUB
PNG_FILTER_UP
PNG_FILTER_AVG
PNG_FILTER_PAETH
PNG_ALL_FILTERS
</para>
</refsect1>


